{"title":"【060】伪类选择器","slug":"hell0-world8","date":"2022-10-01T04:11:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:14:59.765Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world8.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                Document        a:link {        color: red;    }a:visited &#123;    color: green;&#125; a:hover &#123;    color: purple;&#125;a:active &#123;    color: yellow;&#125;div &#123;    width: 200px;    height: 200px;    background-color: skyblue;&#125;div:hover &#123;    background-color: red;&#125;div:active &#123;    width； 100px;    height: 100px;&#125;        “五育并举” 全面发展素质教育<br><br>","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Document</title>\n    <style>\n    a:link {\n        color: red;\n    }\n\n<pre><code>a:visited &#123;\n    color: green;\n&#125; \n\na:hover &#123;\n    color: purple;\n&#125;\n\na:active &#123;\n    color: yellow;\n&#125;\n\ndiv &#123;\n    width: 200px;\n    height: 200px;\n    background-color: skyblue;\n&#125;\n\ndiv:hover &#123;\n    background-color: red;\n&#125;\n\ndiv:active &#123;\n    width； 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n&#125;\n</code></pre>\n<p></style></p>\n</head>\n<body>\n<a href=\"#\">\n        “五育并举” 全面发展素质教育\n</a><br><br>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<div>\n    你若盛开，蝴蝶自来\n</div>\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <h3></h3><br>\n鼠标点击前：：link<br><br>\n鼠标点击后：:visited<br><br>\n鼠标悬停时：:hover<br><br>\n鼠标点击时：:active<br><br>\n注意：<br><br>\n1.冒号和后面的鼠标行为，没有任何空格，必须连接在一起；<br><br>\n2.4个伪类选择器须按以上顺序书写；否则浏览器中部分样式不能实现；<br><br>\n3.伪类选择器全部一起使用的情况，主要应用在超链接上，偶尔也会独立使用在其它标签上。<br><br>\n4.伪类选择器也可以用在其它元素上，但只能实现active激活瞬间，和hover鼠标悬停效果。<br><br>  \n</body>\n</html> \n","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}